{"tid":1320794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"班狗去左新城拎cctv 琴晚係新城食飯既人注意！","createTime":"2019-07-15T13:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T13:22:31.000Z","uid":198233,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"faeed4cca506a4d35cc70f3ad7606d668fe1c537","tid":1320794,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94MoQ5X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94MoQ5X.png&h=3330d4f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//copy自青年新政// <br />\n<br />\n新城市廣場已經有CID翻睇CCTV了, 大家亦都知新x基同警犬係幾咁老友啦, 所以, 保護自己, 保護戰友, 記得:<br />\n<br />\n- 發夢野餐用過的帽, 衫, 褲, 鞋, 背囊, 摭等都必須銷毀, 警察會認服飾, 認鞋, 認特徵, 所以一定要掉。 安全及可行下, 最好在遠離家中的地方棄置<br />\n- 手機/家中電腦上如有hot zone的相片及影片必須刪除, 通訊軟件或社交網絡對話紀錄如有行動或行蹤資料必須刪除<br />\n- Google或Apple如備有閣下的Location位置資訊, 請將最近幾天行蹤刪除<br />\n- 曾進入hot zone的SIM卡要報失<br />\n- 炎炎盛夏, 係時候改換髮型和嘗試新髮色<br />\n- 仲有, 唔好週圍講, 唔好出post講自己去過咩上水沙田, 發過咩夢, 無人想知啊"},{"pid":"77045f8181fc2ce9ea9ae26ed4901870f214318c","tid":1320794,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b540ac9218eec84c79316f93559e6ae488a7a1e","tid":1320794,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:11:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bd1afa3f2833553e34de0df8918bf9509a377fb","tid":1320794,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcdafe641e3d97f7f32f15374d01ece50474528b","tid":1320794,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49b4bef459cb3fc8f6c44a2dfe6fb38a5af407cc","tid":1320794,"uid":6197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:16:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1651a6b562d4d73abfac58263b5ca0fd02c5c666","tid":1320794,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face